locations.name: Mammoth Cave National Park
locations.description: Mammoth Cave National Park is located in Kentucky and is home to the world's longest known cave system. It also features hiking trails and other outdoor activities.
locations.address: 1 Mammoth Cave Pkwy, Mammoth Cave, KY 42259

locations.name: Jack Daniel's Distillery
locations.description: Jack Daniel's Distillery is located in Lynchburg, TN and offers tours and tastings of its famous whiskey.

locations.name: Rock Island State Park
locations.description: This unique park features the Pottawatomie Lighthouse as well as stone buildings built by a wealthy inventor who owned the island between 1910 and 1964. Rock Island offers rustic, walk-in campsites, hiking trails, a swimming beach and miles of shoreline to explore.

locations.name: Great Smoky Mountains National Park
locations.description: Great Smoky Mountains National Park is located in Tennessee and North Carolina and offers stunning mountain views, hiking trails, and wildlife viewing opportunities.

locations.name: Fall Creek Falls State Park
locations.description: Fall Creek Falls State Park is a 26,000-acre park located in southeastern Tennessee. It features waterfalls, hiking trails, and camping facilities.

locations.name: Tennessee Safari Park
locations.description: A drive-thru zoo with over 400 animals!

locations.name: Unclaimed Baggage
locations.description: The nation's only lost luggage store- shop through people's stuff from their unclaimed baggage at this huge thrift-style store!

locations.name: National Civil Rights Museum At the Lorraine Motel
locations.description: The National Civil Rights Museum, located at the Lorraine Motel, honors and preserves the legacy of Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. We chronicle the American civil rights movement and tell the story of the ongoing struggle for human rights.

locations.name: Graceland
locations.description: Visit Elvis Presley's Memphis at Graceland, our 200,000 square foot entertainment complex featuring museums, restaurants, gift shops, and more.

locations.name: Cookeville Antique Mall
locations.description: A clean and friendly multi-vendor antique mall with over 9000 sq. ft of antique wonders to sift through!

locations.name: Loretta Lynn's Ranch
locations.description: Sit back, relax, and enjoy live music during weekend campfire shows, get a tan by the pool, reel in the big fish, or get wet tubing or kayaking down beautiful Hurricane Creek. Be sure to check out the many gift shop and museums located in Western Town.

locations.name: Chickamauga & Chattanooga National Military Park
locations.description: Park at the site of 2 Civil War battles, featuring trails, visitor centers & an archeological site.
locations.address: 110 Point Park Rd, Lookout Mountain, TN 37350

locations.name: Springfield Antique Barn
locations.description: Springfield's largest antique store with more than 130 Vendors
locations.address: 700 Willow St, Springfield, TN, United States, Tennessee

locations.name: cumberland caverns
locations.description: With almost 30 miles of caves and underground passageways, incredible underground rock formations, beautiful underground waterfalls, and gleaming pools, there is plenty of fun and adventure for everyone!
